						               													<description>The Collapsing Lands are aptly named. Every step you take could see the ground open up like a gaping maw, eager to swallow you whole. But what if there were a hidden world below, filled with secrets and treasures just waiting to be discovered?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;ldquo;On the Edge of Peril&amp;rdquo; is a Kickstarter exclusive expansion offered in the Collector's Edition pledge.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It expands your adventures with new Exploration cards that will hinder your progress until you fight off the danger.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During your adventure, you may be instructed (no spoilers ?) to slip the &amp;ldquo;Peril&amp;rdquo; divider behind the 110 card. Whenever you take a Terrain card stored after that divider (card nr. 111 and up), you must replace 1 Exploration card attached to that terrain with one showing the &amp;ldquo;Peril&amp;rdquo; (skull) icon.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Luckily, you possess a Groundquaker, a powerful artifact stolen from the Necrodruids, which will help you push the divider further back and with it the edge of peril!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
